{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.440", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.480", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber ein Jahr nach dem schlimmsten islamistischen Anschlag in Deutschland soll nun\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich muss sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.920", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.360", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch ein Untersuchungsausschuss auf Bundesebene eingesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.280", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich muss leider sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.280", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das h\u00e4tten wir auch deutlich fr\u00fcher haben k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.960", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Fraktion hat schon im Fr\u00fchjahr\u00a02017 einen entsprechenden Antrag vorgelegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.680", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Grosse-Br\u00f6mer von der CDU/CSU-Fraktion fand es damals laut \u201eBild am Sonntag\u201c peinlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir diesen Antrag vorgelegt haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde es zutiefst peinlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.600", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das muss ich Ihnen ganz ehrlich sagen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.560", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass auf Bundesebene bis heute keine \u00f6ffentlichen und transparenten Aufkl\u00e4rungsschritte in dieser Sache unternommen worden sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt sind Sie endlich auf den Aufkl\u00e4rungszug aufgesprungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.440", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau wie Gr\u00fcne, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.520", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "FDP und Linke haben Union und SPD jetzt auch einen Antrag vorgelegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.200", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber bei der Lekt\u00fcre fragt man sich schon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.920", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob Sie nur auf diesen Zug aufgesprungen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.960", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um ihn gleich wieder abzubremsen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.720", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Harbarth, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.360", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben vorhin gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.520", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie in Ihrem Antrag bewusst auf Detailfragen verzichtet haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es k\u00f6nnten ja vielleicht zu viele unangenehme Details dabei ans Licht kommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern kann ich die Motivation schon nachvollziehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das erkl\u00e4rt wahrscheinlich auch die Forderung in Ihrem Antrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Untersuchungen auf den Zeitraum bis zu dem Todestag von Anis Amri zu begrenzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.840", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alles soll sich auf diese eine Person konzentrieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.600", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich wei\u00df nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.520", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es Ihnen klar ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber damit erweisen Sie ihm posthum genau die Ehre, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.120", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die er sich f\u00fcr sich durch seinen schrecklichen Anschlag gew\u00fcnscht hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.440", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So eine PR k\u00f6nnen wir doch nicht ernsthaft wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.400", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.280", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine noch viel gravierendere Folge dieses Enddatums ist aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.440", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass damit das Handeln der Bundesregierung und der Sicherheitsbeh\u00f6rden nach dem Attentat v\u00f6llig au\u00dfen vor bleibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.720", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber genau hier wird es doch interessant."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.280", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung hat zwar damals mit dem Finger in alle Richtungen gezeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.640", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "doch immer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es um die Verantwortung auf Bundesebene ging, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ging es ab in den Graben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.440", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann mich noch sehr gut an das laute Schweigen des Bundesamtes f\u00fcr Verfassungsschutz erinnern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.760", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bundesinnenminister hat Verfassungsschutzpr\u00e4sident Maa\u00dfen sogar ausdr\u00fccklich abgeraten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.520", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Dezember\u00a02016 im Innenausschuss \u00fcberhaupt zu erscheinen und Fragen zu beantworten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.160", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir hatten damals dar\u00fcber diskutiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.040", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr de Maizi\u00e8re. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen nat\u00fcrlich genau wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.480", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum Sie solche Ratschl\u00e4ge geben und welche Rolle der Verfassungsschutz tats\u00e4chlich gespielt hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen selbstverst\u00e4ndlich wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.760", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob die Bundesregierung das Parlament und die B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger zum Beispiel hinsichtlich der Chronologie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.880", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die \u00fcberall zitiert worden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jederzeit korrekt informiert hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.160", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und wir wollen wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.120", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob nach dem Tod von Amri in seinem Umfeld nach Komplizen gesucht wurde oder warum eine Person, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.640", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der Amri zum Beispiel sehr engen pers\u00f6nlichen Kontakt hatte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anfang\u00a02017 pl\u00f6tzlich abgeschoben wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.800", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen von Union und SPD: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.800", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Machen Sie bitte keine Politik mit dem Enddatum der Untersuchungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.280", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss uns doch um maximale Aufkl\u00e4rung und nicht um Regierungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder Beh\u00f6rdenschutz gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.960", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen doch der Frage nachgehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welche Rolle islamistische Netzwerke und deren Beobachtungen im In- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie im Ausland beim Attentat gespielt haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.400", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch wollen wir die Rolle des Gemeinsamen Terrorismusabwehrzentrums ganz genau kl\u00e4ren und herausarbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sich M\u00e4ngel an der Sicherheitsarchitektur abstellen lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.680", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist vorhin schon einmal gesagt worden: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.080", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das GTAZ existiert seit 2004, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.720", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "doch die Lage hat sich bis heute gravierend ver\u00e4ndert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.680", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.960", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es \u00fcberhaupt noch in unsere Zeit passt oder ob wir nicht dringend notwendige Ver\u00e4nderungen vornehmen m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen Verantwortlichkeiten klar benennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.040", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "egal wo diese vielleicht liegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.800", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00fcssen wir herausarbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.360", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns im Gesch\u00e4ftsordnungsausschuss deshalb nach einer tragf\u00e4higen L\u00f6sung suchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die unserem Aufkl\u00e4rungsanspruch tats\u00e4chlich gerecht wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat der Kollege Armin Schuster f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}